---
---

<section class="section closer">
  <div class="wrap closer__grid">
    <div class="closer__main" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow label">The benchmark</span>
      <h2 class="display closer__title">
        A bad pitch has to score<br />below a good one.
      </h2>
      <p class="closer__sub">
        The scoring isn’t vibes. It runs without a microphone as a plain test: a
        weak pitch must land under a strong one, every time, or the judge isn’t
        trustworthy. It’s held to its own standard before it’s allowed to hold
        you to yours.
      </p>
      <div class="closer__cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#top">Pitch to it →</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://github.com/whereissam/PitchPilot" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read the code</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="proof" data-reveal data-delay="1" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="proof__row">
        <span class="proof__tag">weak pitch</span>
        <span class="proof__bar"><span style="width:30%; background:var(--muted)"></span></span>
        <span class="proof__n mono">3.0</span>
      </div>
      <div class="proof__row">
        <span class="proof__tag">strong pitch</span>
        <span class="proof__bar"><span style="width:80%"></span></span>
        <span class="proof__n mono">8.0</span>
      </div>
      <p class="proof__assert mono">assert weak &lt; strong ✓</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .closer { padding-block: clamp(5rem, 12vh, 9rem); }
  .closer__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .closer__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .closer__sub { font-size: 1.12rem; color: var(--muted); max-width: 46ch; }
  .closer__cta { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.9rem; margin-top: 2rem; }

  .proof {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--paper);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.8rem 1.6rem;
    box-shadow: 10px 12px 0 rgba(40, 52, 122, 0.12);
  }
  .proof__row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 6.5rem 1fr 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }
  .proof__tag { font-size: 0.82rem; opacity: 0.85; }
  .proof__bar {
    height: 9px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .proof__bar span {
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--orange);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .proof__n { font-size: 0.86rem; text-align: right; }
  .proof__assert {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #8ff0bf;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .closer__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .proof { max-width: 460px; }
  }
</style>
